      "title": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Dream Forest Langkawi"
          }
        ]
      },
      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "An Enchanting Rainforest Night WalkWhere legends come to lifeAs night falls, travellers are invited to enter the Dream Forest Book Portal and into the magical realm of Sang Gedembai, the legendary keeper of stories and Guardian of the Forest.Stroll along a leisurely 1.2km trail to discover tales like the bittersweet love story of Dayang Bunting Lake, the fabled battle between mighty warrior Merong Mahawangsa and his nemesis Garuda, and… did you know Langkawi was once the home of GIANTS? Immerse yourself in their stories through mesmerising lights, music, projection mapping, art installations, interactive activities and narration.Created by Tiara Jacquelina and the award-winning team at Enfiniti - storytelling, cutting-edge technology and nature come together to create an unforgettable experience.Are you ready for a magical journey?"
          }
        ]
      },
      "rating": {
        "average_value": 4.5,
        "rating_count": 850
      },
      "product_features": [
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Stroll along a leisurely 1.2km trail to discover Langkawi's mythical tales, brought to life through mesmerising lights, music, projection mapping"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "The 14 different zones are carefully designed around the natural environment and tell stories about Langkawi's rich history and folklore including the Legend."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "This magical multi-sensory adventure is perfect for families with children of all ages."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "There are discounts for Langkawi residents, MyKad holders, and senior citizens."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "The park is open from 7:00 pm to 11:30 pm on Sunday through Tuesday and Thursday through Saturday. It is closed on Wednesdays unless it is a public or school holiday."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "How to get there: reach Dream Forest Langkawi by car or motorcycle via Langkawi's main roads; parking and motorcycle parking are available near the entrance."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Escape the ordinary and enter a world of wonder on Langkawi's Enchanting Night Walk! Step through a dreamlike portal and embark on a leisurely stroll through the rainforest. Uncover captivating local legends like the star-crossed lovers of Dayang Bunting Lake and the epic battle between Merong Mahawangsa and Garuda. Interactive displays, mesmerizing lights, music, and projections bring these stories to life. Created by the award-winning Enfiniti team, this unforgettable experience blends storytelling with cutting-edge technology for a magical journey through Langkawi's myths and rainforest beauty."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Admission to Dream Forest Langkawi"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Show your mobile ticket at the ticketing counter."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Purchase e-ticket(s) at least 24 hours before your visit; otherwise normal admission charges may apply at the venue. Free admission for children aged 2 and below. Limited Time Offer tickets: Adult 16–59 yrs, Child 3–15 yrs, Senior 60+ yrs. Standard Admission tickets: Adult 13+ yrs, Child 4–12 yrs, Senior 60+ yrs. OKU guests require a valid disability certificate. No outside food or drinks; prohibited items include bottles, firecrackers, lasers, and anything that disturbs other guests. Flash photography is prohibited. No re-entry after you leave. Tickets are non-transferable, not for resale, non-exchangeable, and non-refundable; validity dates cannot be changed."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Free cancellation till validity ends (per vendor policy)."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Age: Best for ages 7+, parental discretion advised."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Food/Drinks: Bring water, check for cafes on-site."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Photography: Flash restrictions may apply."
              }
            ]
          }
        }
